  "title": "Assistant admin manager",
  "description": "<p>Full sets of accounts</p><p>- Xero Accounting software knowledge</p><p>- GST Reporting</p><p>- Microsoft office software e.g. Excel, Word, Powerpoint</p><p>- Payroll and HR related</p><p>- Administrative and ad-hoc duties<br /><br />-packing<br /></p><p>-mom application<br /></p><p>-Claims</p><p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>Proficiency in both Chinese and English languages to effectively communicate with a diverse members.</li><li>Previous experience in an administrative role preferred, if no experience. training will be provided as long have a strong willingness to learn.</li><li>Strong organizational and time management skills, with the ability to multitask and prioritize tasks effectively.</li><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills, with a customer service-oriented approach.</li><li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office Suite (Word, Excel, Outlook).</li><li>Ability to work independently and as part of a team in a fast-paced environment.</li><li>Attention to detail and accuracy in record-keeping and data management.</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li>Competitive salary based on experience.</li><li>Flexible work schedule and supportive work environment.</li><li>Commission Pay</li></ul><p><strong>WORK SCHEDULE:</strong> 5.5 Days Week</p>",
